  "desc": "<p>A powerful group of Bathysmal Vishaps.</p><p>They have been specifically bred and selected by the people of Enkanomiya, which has given them their exceptional strength. Of course, no vishap would consider this some sort of debt to be repaid.</p><p>The strongest members of this herd can use different elements, which they wield as a show of their hatred.</p>",
